settings.subheading: Bright and breezy, Nautical Weave combines crisp patterns with vibrant tropical energy. Perfect for sunny mornings by the water or sunset sails, it brings island charm to every moment.
Cool, contemporary and so on trend, this minty swimwear will add a flattering, fresh, and chic update to your seaside vibe.
There's no better way to show off your sun-kissed skin than by wearing a white suit. Our eco-friendly Textured White is perfect for the bride, or for anyone who wants to make a statement in the sun.
Elevate your style with rich,textured chocolate brown. Inspired by tropical palm trunks, this earthy hue adds warmth and versatility to your wardrobe for day-to-night elegance.

Capture the essence of island life with Paradise Palm. Featuring swaying palm motifs and breezy white sands, this print radiates tranquil, tropical vibes perfect for effortless, sun-soaked adventures.
A fresh twist on summer, our Coral swimsuits will remind you of brilliant tropical sunsets and the magic of vibrant coral reefs.
Our Gigi Floral is a beautiful coral print with bold pink and white accents that provide an air of timeless beauty and femininity.
Nestled in between blue and green, our eco-friendly Seafoam Aqua refreshes your wardrobe like clear, crisp ocean water along a sandy beach
Marbella Tile is your favorite geometric print to pair with our navy, seafoam, white, and sky blue solids. Here comes the sun!

Anything but basic, this delicate Coastal Stripe print pairs perfectly with our black, mint, coastal blue or white solids, and provides understated glamour whether you're lounging poolside or strolling along the beach.
Chic. Classic. Smart. There's something about a black suit that inspires confidence. Always flattering, never boring, perfectly timeless.
Serene and reminiscent of the tranquil hues found along the ocean's edge.  Think calm waters, clear skies, peaceful sophistication.

With its white hues and subtle waves in rich shades of blue, Malibu will take you to the serenity of the coastal landscape in which it was inspired. The perfect print for an effortlessly elegant beach style.
A fun, flirty, floral motif that infuses a tropical jungle vibe into your beach attire.  Unleash exotic playfulness with this stylish, colorful swimwear.
A perfect shade of vibrant pink.

Navy is Helen Jon's signature solid. Our navy has stayed the same since our first season, making it the perfect introduction to our brand. Many of our prints are designed to mix-and-match back to navy—have fun making your own combinations!

settings.text: Inspired by the iconic style and panache that defines the French Riveria of yesteryear, Cap Ferrat epitomizes seaside sophistication with its chic blend of navy and ivory, elegantly presented in a subtle geometric pattern. Bold and sporty, yet timeless and classic, this print will have you speaking French in no time!
Discover a world of natural elegance and sophistication with our eco-friendly Textured Fatigue swimwear.

The earthy cinnamon-brown of our Sand Dunes print evokes the art of hand-blocked Indian design and the luxury of natural textiles transporting you to exotic lands far away…The perfect neutral print you won’t want to be without.

settings.subheading: Our signature print, Tangier is classic and timeless, with a subtle design that adds a splash to any beach wardrobe. This blue and white print pairs beautifully with our navy resort essentials.
The navy version of our Island Batik print is a boho-yet-preppy take on our exotic print. Pairs beautifully with our sky blue or our navy solids. The islands are calling…
You will love the subtle luxury and silky-soft feel of our Sky Blue fabric. Soft, feminine, and as perfect as a cloudless summer day.
Inspired by the beauty found while strolling through the cobblestone streets of Portuguese seaside villages, Montrose takes us back to relaxed afternoons under the Mediterranean sun.
Inspired by our love of vintage Hawaiian fabrics, the exotic vibe of our Island Batik print, in beautiful shades of pink, will take you straight to Waikiki.
